dct_title_s: Property of John Abel, Point Pleasant, New Jersey, surveyed
dct_description_sm: This map depicts the waterfront property of John Abel along the Manasquan River and show property improvements. The map is en verso stamped as received May 10, 1921.
Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection
